\v 38 Zvino mupristi mwanakomana waAroni achava neVaRevhi, VaRevhi pavachatora zvegumi. Zvino VaRevhi vachakwidza chegumi chechegumi kuimba yaMwari wedu\x + Num.. 18.26.\x* kumakamuri eimba\x + 10.38,39. 2 Madz. 23.11.\x* yezvinokosha\x + 1 Makor. 26.20.\x*.
\v 39 Nokuti vana vaIsraeri nevana vaRevhi vachauya nechipo chezviyo\x + 13.12. Det. 12.6,11. 2 Makor. 31.12.\x*, chewaini itsva, nemafuta\x + 10.37. 13.5,12.\x*, kumakamuri\x + 10.38,39. 2 Madz. 23.11.\x*, nokuti imo mune midziyo yeimba tsvene, nevapristi vanoshanda, nevarindi vemikova, nevaimbi. Zvino hatingasii imba yaMwari wedu\x + 13.11.\x*.